        </dd>

        
                <dt>Physical Descriptions</dt>
        <dd>
          <dl>
                          <dt>Medium</dt>
              <dd>Black chalk and gray wash on cream antique laid paper, framing line in brown ink</dd>
            
           
           
                          <dt>Dimensions</dt>
              <dd>23.1 x 13.5 cm (9 1/8 x 5 5/16 in.)</dd>
            
            
            
            
            
                          <dt>Inscriptions and Marks</dt>
              <dd>
